<section>
  <h2 id="publishing-on-the-web-topics">Publishing on the Web Topics</h2>

  <ol>
    <li>Static Sites</li>
    <li>Content Management Systems</li>
    <li>Niche Services:</li>
  </ol>

</section>
<ul>
  <li>Static Sites
    <ul>
      <li><em>classic</em> hosting (NYU Libraries web hosting)</li>
      <li>services (GitHub Pages, Netlify, etc.)</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>Content Management Systems
    <ul>
      <li>hosted vs self hosted / on premise / &quot;local&quot;</li>
      <li>popular: WordPress, Omeka</li>
      <li>others: Readymag, Squarespace, Wix</li>
      <li>CMS/plus: Joomla, Drupal</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>Niche Services:
    <ul>
      <li>Story Maps</li>
      <li>AirTable</li>
      <li>Online Counterpart of Desktop Tools (Tableau Online, ArcGIS Online)</li>
      <li>Other: https://observablehq.com/</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>

